Long Audio Alignment
--------------------
This package contains the basic framework for testing Audio aligners , 
as well as some utils to do string manipulations for removing unaccounted 
characters from transcription files and pronunciation generator for OOV
words.

For running current version of aligner, we recommend the use of ANT.
Following should be your directory structure:

Parent Directory/
	|
	|-------Project_Directory/
	|	|
	|	|-------bin/
	|	|	
	|	|-------build/
	|	|
	|	|-------resource/
	|	|	|
